1
00:00:08,916 --> 00:00:10,305
None of us really know each other.

2
00:00:11,985 --> 00:00:13,694
We're all screw-ups.

3
00:00:14,618 --> 00:00:15,905
But somehow ...

4
00:00:17,498 --> 00:00:19,752
We were all in the same place at the same time

5
00:00:19,750 --> 00:00:21,003
when Billy found those coins.

6
00:00:24,109 --> 00:00:26,407
Guys, check out how we glow.

7
00:00:27,403 --> 00:00:28,312
I'm blue!

8
00:00:29,309 --> 00:00:30,400
I'm black!

9
00:00:30,705 --> 00:00:32,007
-What?
-I am!

10
00:00:32,101 --> 00:00:33,003
No, you're not!

11
00:00:36,705 --> 00:00:37,789
You felt weird?

12
00:00:38,734 --> 00:00:39,672
We're strong.

13
00:00:40,923 --> 00:00:41,927
Insanely strong.

14
00:00:44,101 --> 00:00:46,261
The answer to what is happening to you

15
00:00:46,523 --> 00:00:47,294
is here.

16
00:00:49,061 --> 00:00:50,116
You five ...

17
00:00:50,690 --> 00:00:52,581
Are the Power Rangers.

18
00:00:53,890 --> 00:00:55,825
Did I just hear say we're Power Rangers?

19
00:00:55,820 --> 00:00:56,901
Is this some kinda joke?

20
00:00:56,900 --> 00:00:57,803
We're talking to a wall.

21
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:59,898
I was kind of expecting a little more.

22
00:01:02,545 --> 00:01:03,585
So where were you last night?

23
00:01:04,930 --> 00:01:06,676
Me and 4 kids found a

24
00:01:06,670 --> 00:01:08,676
spaceship buried underground.

25
00:01:09,170 --> 00:01:10,545
I'm pretty sure I'm a superhero.

26
00:01:10,945 --> 00:01:11,556
Cool!

27
00:01:12,196 --> 00:01:13,396
Pee in that cup!

28
00:01:13,709 --> 00:01:16,603
Power Rangers were a legion of Warriors.

29
00:01:17,236 --> 00:01:20,029
You must become those warriors.

30
00:01:20,020 --> 00:01:22,232
It's just a hologram like a video-game.

31
00:01:23,621 --> 00:01:25,243
That's a strong-ass hologram.

32
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,065
Not a video-game.

33
00:01:29,214 --> 00:01:30,494
You were born for this.

34
00:01:31,898 --> 00:01:33,890
I will destroy everything.

35
00:01:36,894 --> 00:01:38,589
She is pure evil.

36
00:01:42,407 --> 00:01:43,694
How d'you expect us to stop her?

37
00:01:45,505 --> 00:01:47,003
It's morphin' time.

38
00:01:59,010 --> 00:02:00,007
That's a lotta gold.

39
00:02:01,214 --> 00:02:03,003
This is your destiny.

40
00:02:06,349 --> 00:02:07,003
Let's go!

41
00:02:07,301 --> 00:02:07,709
Go!

42
00:02:10,232 --> 00:02:12,189
This is your time.

43
